(371, 1, '2013-08-26 18:58:11', '2013-08-26 18:58:11', '[cro_callout text="Add photo galleries with ease and benefit from our unique gallery lightbox." layout="1" color="1"]\n\nWith the assistance of our shortcode manager, galleries can be added to any pages or posts, without breaking a sweat.\n\n[cro_gallery no="0"]\n<h5>Galleries can be added with 5 easy steps.</h5>\n<ol>\n	<li>Create a category to group all the gallery items that belong together.</li>\n	<li>Add your gallery posts.</li>\n	<li>Add your gallery category to the post.</li>\n	<li>Click to open your shortcode manager.</li>\n	<li>Insert the gallery shortcode.</li>\n</ol>\n<a href="http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/galleryprocess.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-376" alt="galleryprocess" src="http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/galleryprocess.jpg" width="768" height="595" /></a>', 'Adding Galleries', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'adding-galleries', '', '', '2013-08-26 18:58:11', '2013-08-26 18:58:11', '', 0, 'http://copy.cro.ma/sport/?page_id=371', 0, 'page', '', 0),
